<title>USA: PDG Environmental plans $2 mln placement.</title>
<headline>PDG Environmental plans $2 mln placement.</headline>
<dateline>MONROEVILLE, Pa. 1996-10-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>PDG Environmental Inc said Friday it planned to raise at least $2 million through a private equity offering of its securities.</p>
<p>The company said it will use the proceeds for working capital, to reduce debt and for future acquisitions.</p>
<p>PDG Environmental provides asbestos abatement and related services.</p>
